Objective
In order to exchange data between various systems, LendingPad developed this guide to allow

system-to-system (S2S) data exchanges for mutual clients. Highlighted fields below are the

critical data points needed for bi-directional push/pull with outside 3rd-party systems. They

include loan level data, key status dates and other participants information. Over time the data

set will be expanded with revised versions of this guide.

LendingPad uses basic authentication with whitelist IP’s or domain names for communication.

Key Information
Test Environment URL: https://testapi.lendingpad.com
Login Credentials: [to be assigned by LendingPad support team]
Live Environment URL: https://api.lendingpad.com
Login Credentials: [to be assigned by LendingPad support team]
"Import” method allows 3rd-party systems to create/add a new loan record in LendingPad.

"Export” method allows LendingPad to update 3rd-party systems every minute with changes.

