MISMO 3.4 Extension

LendingPad supports the import of additional information provided in the MISMO 3.4 file. The

extension information should be added to a loan record with loan role type “SubjectLoan.”

Example:

<EXTENSION>
<OTHER>
<LENDINGPAD>
<CRITICAL_DATES>
