Export Loan Document API Request
The system sends the loan document that contains file and key parameters to 3rd-party servers.

Please create a method that can handle the multipart form data request from the LendingPad.

Please provide the URL and basic authorization information.

The POST method should return status code 200 in response if the request headers contain

‘X-TEST’ header. The request with this header is a test request that includes the sample data

the 3rd party should not handle. LendingPad uses this type of request to validate the connection

between the LendingPad and the 3rd party is active.

